P_HTM[2120]='*568. Sahajāta-nissaya-atthi-avigatanti  nahetuyā nava, naārammaṇe nava, naadhipatiyā  nava, naanantare nava, nasamanantare nava, naaññamaññe pañca, naupanissaye nava…pe… namagge nava, nasampayutte pañca, navippayutte tīṇi, nonatthiyā nava, novigate nava.*';
